### BUILD ###
adjust camera_number in missile.cpp
make all
# build with g++ instead of clang++
# 1) change CXX from clang++ to g++
# 2) remove warning flags -W*
# 3) build

### RUN ###
make sure your camera and missile launcher are connected
make sure that you have the necessary privileges to access camera and launcher (eg use sudo)
in case you use sudo: make sure, that root is allowed to display windows in your x-session (eg xhost +localhost)
run ./USBMissile

### ABORT ###
focus camera window and press ESC
